<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Facilities</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Facilities.css">
</head>

<body>

    <div class="facilities">

        <p class="tag">
            ✨ What You Get
        </p>

        <h2>
            Everything You Need
            <br>
            Under One Roof
        </h2>

        <div class="facility-list">

            <div class="facility-item">
                <h3>High-speed Wifi</h3>
                <p>
                    Stay connected with our reliable high-speed wifi,
                    perfect for work and entertainment.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="facility-item">
                <h3>24/7 Security</h3>
                <p>
                    Feel safe and secure with our round-the-clock
                    security measures and surveillance.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="facility-item">
                <h3>Food and Mess</h3>
                <p>
                    Enjoy delicious and nutritious meals with our
                    convenient food and mess services.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="facility-item">
                <h3>Housekeeping</h3>
                <p>
                    Keep your living space clean and tidy with our
                    regular housekeeping services.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="facility-item">
                <h3>Parking Facilities</h3>
                <p>
                    Convenient parking facilities available for
                    residents and visitors.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="facility-item">
                <h3>24/7 Power Backup</h3>
                <p>
                    Never worry about power outages with our reliable
                    24/7 power backup system.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>